EVERMORE CHEMICA said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 6.37% to NT$125,590,000 from NT$134,129,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            125,590          134,129    
YOY%              -6.37%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            942,925         1,018,800   
YOY%              -7.45% 
=================================================================
 